reviewText: Love the show! Can't wait to get season 4! Shipping was fast even tho it was standard. Thanks to the seller.

It is such a good show. Order was just as expected. In great condition. Shipped very quickly and would order again. Thanks for your great job.

I'd never heard of Scandal until recently as I typically don't watch television. Since friends raved about how good the series was I ordered the first three seasons. I can hardly stop watching it and am enjoying great entertainment experiences..
Disappointed seems to bounce around to much.

This series is so enjoyable and entertaining that I kept wanting to watch episode after episode! It moves along very quickly, filled with lots of action, intrigue, surprises, and extremely interesting characters and situations. I highly recommend it!
So far, so good. Fast shipment. Great price.
More love is less politics. Or is this the other way around.
You can but these seasons individually for ~ $40  Why would I pay an extra 15$ for these 3 discs?
I love love Scandal. Now I can watch them whenever I want to.
